Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.06,0:00:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好~藤本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.49,0:00:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.97,0:00:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道現在幾點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.20,0:00:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.77,0:00:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天天早晨都這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.99,0:00:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.03,0:00:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我又來幫忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.64,0:00:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.78,0:00:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我來幫籐本先生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.24,0:00:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.99,0:00:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.18,0:00:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 小鳩 籐本君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.07,0:00:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.99,0:00:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也要幫忙的?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.66,0:00:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.63,0:00:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本君一定輕鬆了很多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.53,0:00:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑 為什麼我非得讓人幫我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.90,0:00:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩 一定不要大意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.27,0:00:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看籐本君這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.24,0:00:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個沒盯好他又要蠻幹了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的

Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.29,0:01:10.89,logo,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}KTXP&SD字幕組
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.81,0:01:06.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}どうすうればいいんだっけ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.81,0:01:06.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\fad(300,300)}該怎麼辦才好來著?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.87,0:01:11.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}あたりまえのことっていつも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.87,0:01:11.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\fad(300,300)}理所當然的事情總是這麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.00,0:01:14.93,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}難しいな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.00,0:01:14.93,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}紛繁複雜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.34,0:01:17.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}嬉しいとき笑って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.34,0:01:17.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}只是想開心的時候就笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.31,0:01:22.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}好きなときに歌いたいだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.31,0:01:22.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}想唱歌的時候就唱歌而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.08,0:01:25.57,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}なのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.08,0:01:25.57,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}可是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.51,0:01:31.01,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}いつか願いは叶うと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.51,0:01:31.01,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}常說願望總會實現
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.66,0:01:38.25,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}でもいつかってどれくらい待ちきれないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.66,0:01:38.25,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}可是總會到底要多久　已經等不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.62,0:01:41.25,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}１ ２ ３　の合図で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.62,0:01:41.25,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}看好1 2 3的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.57,0:01:44.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}両手　ひろげて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.57,0:01:44.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}張開雙臂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.44,0:01:49.36,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}全身に　光をあつめて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.44,0:01:49.36,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}让全身充满光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.47,0:01:51.98,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}どこに　あるの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.47,0:01:51.98,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}告訴我在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.35,0:01:55.49,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}教えて私にできること
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.35,0:01:55.49,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我能做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.78,0:01:58.31,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}目一杯　傷ついて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.78,0:01:58.31,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}傷得滿目瘡痍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.62,0:02:01.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}精一杯　走って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.62,0:02:01.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}跑的精疲力盡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.42,0:02:05.59,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}何十回　転んで泣いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.42,0:02:05.59,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}幾十次摔倒哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.90,0:02:08.22,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}それでもまた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.90,0:02:08.22,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}即使是這樣還
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.57,0:02:12.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}あきれるくらい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.57,0:02:12.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}難以置信地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.74,0:02:16.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}明日を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.74,0:02:16.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}相信著明天

