Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.36,0:02:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天一天地...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我找到了這個 貼在這裡了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.74,0:02:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 別擅自...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.29,0:02:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有其他事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}[...小鳩的願望.]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要去哪裡呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.96,0:03:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天去了圖書館 前天去了大學裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兼職
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說兼職已經請假了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過多少次了 同情...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.47,0:03:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是同情也不是好奇心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.45,0:03:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了你很煩人了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.85,0:03:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本先生有出去散步過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散步很好 很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.50,0:03:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得有趣的...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.53,0:03:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只有你覺得而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 去有趣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.06,0:03:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 他們兩個一起出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.03,0:03:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要時間呢 不管對誰來說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你們兩個一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想幹什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本先生的這裡 總是皺在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想讓籐本先生能開心一點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.09,0:04:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有小船
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本先生一起去坐小船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那些小船...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.28,0:04:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(出租小船)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.02,0:04:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.02,0:04:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像得花錢...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.33,0:05:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀咧呀咧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.67,0:05:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.43,0:05:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要撞上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.18,0:05:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換我來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.39,0:05:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 籐本先生傷還沒好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照你這樣劃 就永遠回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.28,0:05:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩會加油的 會加油劃的!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.04,0:05:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要讓船槳進到水裡太深
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.14,0:05:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.29,0:05:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把腳也用上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.64,0:05:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.85,0:05:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 船動了 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.68,0:05:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是夠悠閒的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.27,0:05:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.91,0:05:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.31,0:06:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡稍微好一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.91,0:06:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.92,0:06:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 想讓籐本先生恢復些精神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.13,0:06:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來一起去給魚先生餵吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.20,0:06:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是問你這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.45,0:06:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道現在是什麼情況嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.05,0:06:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 又讓籐本先生花錢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這次我拿回零錢了...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了不是問你這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為我在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說已經沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.36,0:06:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 所以我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.76,0:06:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.59,0:06:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我的話還沒說完 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魚先生 吃飯了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.31,0:06:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.00,0:06:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本先生也試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.03,0:06:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我一個人呆會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.88,0:07:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老是跟著的話 我靜不下心來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.93,0:07:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧 小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.15,0:07:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快去收集幾個金平糖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.02,0:07:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.18,0:07:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.73,0:07:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 這不是琥珀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.57,0:07:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在散步嗎 今天天氣確實很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.34,0:07:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不緊不慢的氣氛怎麼這麼強烈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們都是不緊不慢的 幫我說說這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說小鳩小姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.13,0:07:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 把自己的願望都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.54,0:07:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晃晃悠悠不緊不慢地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.43,0:07:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒忘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.05,0:07:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.57,0:08:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的願望已經決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.74,0:08:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.19,0:08:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 那當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 土鳩那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.66,0:08:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就是個土鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.68,0:08:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在生氣嗎 五百祗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.35,0:08:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然在生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.23,0:08:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.39,0:08:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是看到她的那樣的表情...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.16,0:09:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩小姐已經做出了選擇了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個傻瓜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.83,0:09:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生的事情都是必然的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.49,0:09:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 沒有任何一件事是沒有意義的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.69,0:09:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指天界裡嗎 對異界的人也適用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.13,0:09:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是什麼樣的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,適用於所有的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.10,0:09:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.15,0:09:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.87,0:09:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你總抓著我不放
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.01,0:09:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是指...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想得到我的感謝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.91,0:09:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你可找錯門了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你並沒有什麼感激之情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.77,0:09:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將來也不會有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.13,0:10:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為籐本先生是我重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會在意重要的人是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.22,0:10:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管風琴 現在由清花老師保管著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.33,0:10:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.81,0:10:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於籐本先生來說 那是件重要的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.41,0:10:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣想彈的話隨時可以去彈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.74,0:10:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.85,0:10:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得籐本先生和五百祗先生很像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.77,0:10:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如總是很生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.47,0:10:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗 是你一直帶在身邊的布偶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.98,0:10:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.36,0:10:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 其實是個很好的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.26,0:10:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.43,0:10:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.24,0:10:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.61,0:11:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也做出了選擇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.05,0:11:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 你怎麼洗衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.78,0:11:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晾洗好的衣服很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.33,0:11:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.55,0:11:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天不能陪你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.97,0:12:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是再好不過了 終於能解放了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.66,0:12:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本先生能感到高興的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.68,0:12:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.98,0:12:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 是這樣啊 很倉促呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝平日的照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.54,0:12:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也想和千帆和千世打個招呼...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.47,0:12:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們一定會感到寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.43,0:12:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有對清花說嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.07,0:12:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正打算去說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.39,0:12:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.95,0:13:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩來到我家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.20,0:13:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經有一年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.94,0:13:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四個季節
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.06,0:13:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天也好 夏天也好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋天也好 冬天也好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.63,0:13:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個季節都過得很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安頓下來的話 記得聯絡我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 安頓下來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.19,0:13:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的願望已經決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 土鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.23,0:13:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道那意味著什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.26,0:13:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.27,0:13:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不把金平糖集滿的話你就...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.67,0:13:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己會怎樣已經無所謂了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.99,0:13:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是傻瓜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:13:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是傻瓜嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.80,0:14:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是傻瓜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.24,0:14:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一百分滿分的傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.11,0:14:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打好招呼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.93,0:14:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀咧呀咧 他還沒有回來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.51,0:14:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊 月亮很明亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.76,0:15:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.65,0:15:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事 五百祗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.98,0:15:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不做只是陪伴在他身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會感到痛苦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.74,0:15:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.46,0:15:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.74,0:15:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能僅僅陪伴在他身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.09,0:15:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是件非常難得的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.25,0:15:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.65,0:15:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為你已經聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.72,0:15:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩可能是說不出口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.53,0:15:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有說去哪了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.78,0:15:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.32,0:15:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只說安頓下來就會聯繫我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.03,0:15:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.47,0:16:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.32,0:16:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已經很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.71,0:16:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是有點傻有點笨有點缺根筋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.79,0:16:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了開朗和直率毫無可取之處
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.66,0:16:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是作為一個人已經算是很好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.83,0:16:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的靈魂真的已經算很好的了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.19,0:16:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以求求你 讓她消失這件事...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.26,0:16:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她消失這件事...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.15,0:17:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生 兔子先生很困擾的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.56,0:17:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.25,0:17:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要道歉 這是我自己決定的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 五百祗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.99,0:17:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.33,0:17:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.41,0:17:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.27,0:18:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在開玩笑嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.27,0:18:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到最後還讓你生氣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.82,0:18:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.10,0:18:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不說就走掉了 你是什麼意思啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.41,0:18:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.49,0:18:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我說的話讓你不開心了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 完全不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.75,0:18:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.11,0:18:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是契約啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.59,0:18:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡啊 這裡 箱子上面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.60,0:18:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.80,0:18:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是五百祗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...布偶...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.22,0:18:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是裝成布偶而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.41,0:18:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說契約對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.67,0:18:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩 給他看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.92,0:18:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 什麼意思啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.04,0:19:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.64,0:19:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.65,0:19:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈魂之冠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.40,0:19:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的小鳩的靈魂是不屬於任何一個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.67,0:19:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不代表任何生命的曖昧存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.16,0:19:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是根據和某位高權重人士的契約
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.58,0:19:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到了可以重生一次 重新生活的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.15,0:19:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 這到底是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.55,0:19:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩放棄了契約
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.68,0:19:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選擇了在剩下的時間裡 和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.70,0:19:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以契約被打破了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.19,0:19:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我 必須消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的吧 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.92,0:19:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能在籐本先生的身邊真的很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.11,0:20:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真沒用呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來最後想笑著告別的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.46,0:20:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.12,0:20:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊 求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.87,0:20:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本先生是...我最重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.30,0:20:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.21,0:20:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.76,0:20:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.72,0:20:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.22,0:21:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金平糖?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.09,0:21:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.15,0:21:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金平糖...滿了...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.97,0:21:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩的願望改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.54,0:21:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是契約是不能改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.76,0:21:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去想去的地方...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.64,0:21:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本先生的...金平糖...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.30,0:21:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.36,0:21:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這簡直就像是詛咒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.17,0:21:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你 讓小鳩轉生到這個世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.33,0:22:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.99,0:22:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我什麼也做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.74,0:22:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別道歉 我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.30,0:22:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和她在一起時間最長的我...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.70,0:22:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼也做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.97,0:22:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 發生的事全部都是必然的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.92,0:22:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.70,0:22:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須要去我該去的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.72,0:22:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.97,0:22:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等...

Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.21,0:24:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}[明天到來的日子...]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.21,0:23:11.81,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}なくしたものと あつめたものの狭間に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.21,0:23:11.81,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}所失與所得的縫隙中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.42,0:23:20.26,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}あなたの笑顔　落ちていたの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.42,0:23:20.26,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}遺落著你的笑顏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.65,0:23:26.04,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}届きそうで　届かない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.65,0:23:26.04,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}彷彿伸手可及卻又遙不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.23,0:23:31.99,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}飛んでゆけるわけじゃないし
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.23,0:23:31.99,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}飛又飛不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.15,0:23:38.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}笑わせてあげたいだけなのに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.15,0:23:38.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我只是想讓你有更多笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.43,0:23:43.55,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}役立たずのこの翼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.43,0:23:43.55,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}這沒用的雙翼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.88,0:23:49.32,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}何のためにあるのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.88,0:23:49.32,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}到底為什麼存在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.09,0:23:55.73,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}あなたの傍で笑うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.09,0:23:55.73,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我會在你身邊微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.01,0:24:00.57,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}私に出来ること
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.01,0:24:00.57,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}這是我能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.06,0:24:07.41,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}暖めるだけでもいいのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.06,0:24:07.41,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}哪怕給你一絲溫暖也好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.66,0:24:12.03,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}せめて包みたい
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.66,0:24:12.03,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}至少想包容著你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.49,0:24:19.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}気付くの　そのための翼と
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.49,0:24:19.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}終於發覺 雙翼是為此存在
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.55,0:24:27.89,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}今こそわたし　笑うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.55,0:24:27.89,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}所以我現在 在微笑
